div.div: `Refactor GitHub Actions workflow for pytest and autopublish`
chore: remove obsolete test workflow configuration

Refactor TPUFlashAttention for improved memory efficiency and block processing
- Restructured input reshaping and block processing in TPUFlashAttention to optimize memory usage. - Enhanced attention score computation with dynamic slicing for better performance. - Updated attention mask handling to support dynamic block sizes. - Improved output accumulation and reshaping for final output consistency.
Enhance TPUGEMMLinear for FP8 support and input handling
- Modified TPUGEMMLinear to support FP8 quantization and optimized kernel initialization. - Improved input handling to flatten and reshape inputs for matrix multiplication. - Added scale parameters for FP8 operations and adjusted bias handling.
Revamp TPUMultiHeadAttention with flash attention integration
- Integrated flash attention mechanism into TPUMultiHeadAttention for performance optimization. - Updated attention projection layers and reshaping logic for multi-head attention. - Enhanced dropout handling during attention computation.
Refactor DuckDBLogger for improved logging and metrics handling
- Streamlined DuckDBLogger initialization and table creation logic. - Enhanced metrics logging with conflict resolution for duplicate entries. - Improved experiment summary retrieval and CSV export functionality.
Revise VishwamAI model architecture for clarity and efficiency
- Simplified model setup and attention computation methods. - Enhanced transformer block implementation with gradient checkpointing support. - Updated output projection and normalization layers for better performance.
Add model loading utilities for Gemma weights
- Implemented utilities for downloading and converting Gemma model weights from Hugging Face Hub. - Added parameter name mapping for compatibility between PyTorch and JAX formats. - Created a main function for loading pretrained weights with error handling.
feat: Enhance model and pipeline with memory optimizations for improved efficiency
